Details:
Well, here it is. My remake of Blood Gulch. There are some minor bugs in it (mostly shadows and lighting), but since im not getting anywhere trying to fix them i am just going to release it as-is, and re-release it if i ever fix the problems. Specs:
24 spawns per side, full buyzones, teles in the original locations, the cave, custom skybox (DL here)
Please visit Clan 5k3's studio for more Halo css maps and materials.
